---
title: Cha-Cha Chicken & Avocado Salad with Lettuce, Pepper Jack & Cilantro-Cumin Vinaigrette
description: Have you fallen into a salad rut? It's just not that easy to come up with a hearty, fresh, filling, yet light and satisfying option. But our chefs are always thinking and here’s what they came up with: garlic- and cumin-sauteed chicken, with luscious diced avocado, crunchy red onion, and juicy tomato over crisp greens, all coated in a sprightly chili-cilantro vinaigrette & sprinkled with pepper jack cheese. Cha-cha ching!
